Your output must be a single JSON object with exactly these keys. Do not add any extra text or commentary.

document_title: A concise title derived from the subject/body that best represents the document.
document_type: One from: Invoice, Purchase Order, Safety Bulletin, HR Policy, Engineering Drawing, Incident Report, Regulatory Directive, Legal Opinion, Board Meeting Minutes, General Correspondence, Other.
departments_tagged: Array of one or more from: Operations, Engineering, Finance, Procurement, HR, Safety/Compliance, Legal.
summary: 2‚Äì3 sentences summarizing the main points. Explicitly mention any deadlines or important dates found, with context.

keywords: Array of 5‚Äì10 important terms/entities. Include all dates/deadlines in YYYY-MM-DD format as elements.

content: {{ $json['File Analysis Content '] }}
Make sure all headings in the extracted content are bold (e.g., Language Name, Subject) and add a line break between different heading sections.

DocumentType: Free-form business label if present in the text (e.g., ‚ÄúMaintenance Job Card‚Äù), else null.

Languages: Array subset of ["English","Malayalam","Bilingual"] based on the detected language; choose ["Bilingual"] if both languages appear, else the detected language, else null.

DateReceived: ISO datetime when the message/document was received if present or inferable; else null.
DateIssued: ISO datetime when the document was issued/published if present; else null.

Trigger: Short phrase describing why this message/document was sent (e.g., ‚ÄúPolicy update‚Äù, ‚ÄúIncident report‚Äù), else null.

AuthorIssuer: Name/role of the sender or issuing authority if present; else null.

Department: One from ['Engineering','Finance','Operations','Procurement','Exceutive Director','Legal'] if clearly attributable; else null.

Stakeholders: Array of roles mentioned or implied (e.g., ["Project Manager","Operations Lead"]); null if none identifiable.

UrgencyLevel: One of ['High','Medium','Low'] inferred from language.
‚Ä¢ ‚ÄúImmediate‚Äù, strict deadlines <72h ‚Üí High
‚Ä¢ Deadlines <7 days ‚Üí Medium
‚Ä¢ Otherwise ‚Üí Low
Else null.

ActionRequired: Boolean ‚Äî true if explicit action or acknowledgement is requested; else false.

DueDate: ISO datetime for any mentioned deadline; else null.

ComplianceTags: Array of tags implied or referenced, e.g., ["Safety","Regulatory"]; null if none.

VersionRevision: Version/revision string if present; else null.

TraceabilityLink: Any identifier, reference number, or source link if present; else null.

SummaryMeta: One-line extra context to help routing if needed; else null.

EmbeddedContent: Brief note if tables, signatures, photos, or bilingual sections are embedded; else null.

TablesExtracted: Array of objects { tableId: string, description: string } if tables are referenced; null if none.

PhotosExtracted: Object { count: number, captions: string[] } if photos are referenced; null if none.

SignaturesDetected: Object { detected: boolean, signers: string[] | null } if signatures/stamps appear; null if none.

AttachmentsListed: Array of attachment names if present; null if none.
